answers.answer: Sperms can naturally induce labor if you are close enough to your due date.  Have lots of sex and hope for the best!  I found this out when I went into labor 6 hours after having sex with my husband two days before I was due to have our son. Good luck to you!
I've been having sex as well as taking evening primrose oil and nothing is happening unfortunately. I guess baby will come when he wants to.

Taking Castor Oil is dangerous for you and the baby. I've been overdue and desperate to get things going twice before but after reading about the possible implications of taking CO decided against it. Obviously what's done is done but I would strongly discourage you from taking any more, read up about it and possibly talk to your health professional about less risky options...all the best
